# ğŸ“„ DocRAG LLM  
**Docling â†’ Chroma â†’ Ollama: Simple Local RAG Pipeline**  

[![PyPI](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/docrag-llm)](https://pypi.org/project/docrag-llm/)  
